replies.body:
Indeed...

Tank junglers can have a mini {{item:3068}} 
AP fighter junglers can have a mini {{item:3100}} 
Autoattacking junglers can have a mini {{item:3091}} that becomes huge when well farmed
AD caster junglers can have a mini {{item:3071}} 

Why can't fiddle have a mini {{item:3157}} or at least a mini {{item:3174}} as his jungle item? Maybe tied to farm a la Devourer?
(E.g. you need 30 stacks to unlock the stasis active, or the %mp5 passive scales with the number of stacks up to a cap)

Not counting that other junglers could use them too: {{champion:131}} might situationally prefer the mini Zhonya to Runeglaive, {{champion:31}}  may situationally prefer the mini Grail to Cinderhulk, etc...
